properties.name: Eleventh (Last) rappel  from exit
properties.description: Eight rappel is tricky start,  bolts both side,  LDC bolts more fun,  70ft in water course. Possible to split that as 55 and 15. Ninth rappel 20 ft both side bolts. Left side thru crack water course,  might damage localites water pipelines. Right is courtesy. Tenth rappel 80 ft. Bolt in wired location. We used tree a little off to RDC. Eleventh rappel 230 ft,  twin bolts RDC. Can be split but,  second set bolts in awkward position.
